Item
An item object represents an item being sold by the Vending Machine.

The RegularVendingMachine class represents a regular vending machine created by the vending machine factory.

VendingMachineController
The VendingMachineController class handles the user interactions with the vending machine.
VendingMachineModel
The VendingMachineModel represents the business layer of the vending machine factory and the individual vending machines that will be created.
VendingMachineView
The VendingMachineView class represents the graphical user interface (GUI) for a vending machine.
